The paper deals with similarity searches on vectorial data, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves a novel space-efficient trie data structure, which falls under the category of data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the use of sketches in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) applications.
